  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The apartments are based on self-catering but you've got the option to upgrade to half board and eat at the Hotel Banchetta. There's a hot and cold buffet breakfast and a four-course evening meal with choices. There's also a candle-lit dinner once a week.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Banchetta Apartments are in the centre of Borgata, a small village four kilometres from <a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/%7blocalLink:umb:/document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea%7d" title="Sestriere">Sestriere</a>. The lifts are only 300 metres away so getting into Sestriere or straight up on to the mountain and the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/italy/milky-way-ski-area/sauze-doulx">Milky Way</a> each day is nice and easy. The lifts here often don't have queues, which makes for a dream start each morning. You can ski right back to the building along one of the paths from the main slopes, too. Borgata is the perfect place to experience the local way of life which is centred around a small number of bars and restaurants.</p>
<p>The apartments are located behind <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/italy/milky-way-ski-area/sestriere/hotel-banchetta">Hotel Banchetta</a>. They're basic and snug in size but come with a handy kitchenette. If you want to upgrade to half board, you can eat at the Hotel Banchetta. You can also pay to use their sauna.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 45 mins by coach from Turin airport.</p>]]></description>
